17
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,333
What are you doing there?

18
00:01:11,467 --> 00:01:13,433
The storm is coming!
Go home!

19
00:01:15,233 --> 00:01:16,167
[MAN] Grace!

20
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:19,433
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

21
00:01:19,567 --> 00:01:26,533
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

22
